Our Commission Structure

Simplified Earning structure, Maximum Value
Free
access to the award - winning international student recruitment platform.
No hidden fees, just pure opportunity.
100%
commission for all enrollments in 2,000+ Premium Programs listed on the platform.
Identify this symbol for 100% commission on enrollments.
80%
commission for all enrollments in an extensive selection of programs available on the platform.
maximise your earnings with unlimited potential by joining the Adventus.io platform today.
SIGN UP TODAY

Experience higher rewards with our
commission structure

Unlimited core platform access

With a limit of 5 applications per student.
(*Limit may vary according to the location of the Recruiter.)

Access to exclusive promotions and cashback offers

100% Commission*

For enrollments to Premium Institution Partners

2,000+ Premium Programs available

Access to all destination countries

Including the USA, UK, Australia, New Zealand, Europe, Canada, Malaysia, and more

Operate your company globally*

*For every country, your company should have a registered office. Separate applications and KYC documents are needed for each country expansion.

Administrative fees
For 80% commission enrolments: 4.95% 2.95%
For 100% commission enrolments: 4.95%

*4.95% admin fee will be applicable for Premium Institution Partners enrolments.

FREQUENTLY ASKED

Your questions answered

Accordion Title
Accordion Content
What is the administrative fee?

This is a standard banking and exchange conversion fee charged for processing credits cards and foreign currencies. Despite the standard administrative fee increasing to 4.95%, we are committed to maintaining our competitive transaction fee for our recruiter partners at 2.95%.

Do you have any paid subscriptions?

No, to simplify our offerings, we have removed all subscription tiers. All recruiter partners can enjoy our free subscription plan, earning 80% commission.

What are Premium Institution Partners?

We prioritise matching students with the perfect educational fit, and our Premium Institution Partners are a curated list of top-ranking universities designed to meet diverse aspirations. These institutions offer localised information, dedicated advisory services, and fast turnaround times. Additionally, you will receive 100% commission for successful enrolments to these institutions.
